- name: Spec Example 7.9. Single Quoted Lines
  from: "http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2788756"
  tags: single spec scalar whitespace upto-1.2
  yaml: "' 1st non-empty\n\n 2nd non-empty␣\n———»3rd non-empty '\n"
